 transition-all duration-200 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-slate-900\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe w-4 h-4 text-slate-400\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-xs font-bold tracking-tight\">도메인 기초</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl cursor-pointer transition-all duration-200 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-slate-900\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-triangle-alert w-4 h-4 text-slate-400\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-xs font-bold tracking-tight\">실수 모음</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl cursor-pointer transition-all duration-200 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-slate-900\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-square-check-big w-4 h-4 text-slate-400\"><path d=\"M21 10.5V19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h12.5\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-xs font-bold tracking-tight\">준비 체크</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl cursor-pointer transition-all duration-200 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-slate-900\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-play w-4 h-4 text-slate-400\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polygon points=\"10 8 16 12 10 16 10 8\"></polygon></svg><span class=\"text-xs font-bold tracking-tight\">빠른 체험</span></div></div></div><a class=\"bg-indigo-600 rounded-2xl p-6 space-y-4 shadow-xl shadow-indigo-600/20 text-white relative overflow-hidden group block text-center transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1\" href=\"/faq\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-help w-12 h-12\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 text-white\">도움이 필요하신가요?</h3><div class=\"w-full bg-white text-indigo-600 py-3 rounded-xl text-xs font-black hover:bg-indigo-50 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2 shadow-lg\">FAQ 보러가기 <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div></a></div></aside><div class=\"flex-1 space-y-24 min-w-0 pb-32\"><div class=\"animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-4 duration-700 space-y-20\"><section class=\"space-y-8\"><div class=\"space-y-2 text-center md:text-left\"><span class=\"text-xs font-black text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]\">01. Introduction</span><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight\">이 강의는 무엇인가</h2></div><div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/10 p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl shadow-indigo-500/5 relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 p-8 opacity-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap w-40 h-40 text-indigo-600\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"relative z-10 space-y-8\"><p class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white leading-tight\">👉 코딩을 배우는 강의가 아니라, <span class=\"text-indigo-600\">AI를 활용해 결과물을 만드는 법</span>을 배우는 과정입니다.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 pt-6\"><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 space-y-3 group hover:bg-indigo-600 transition-all duration-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-square w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors\"><path d=\"M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z\"></path></svg><h4 class=\"text-base font-black dark:text-white group-hover:text-white transition-colors tracking-tight\">지시하는 능력</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-bold group-hover:text-indigo-100 transition-colors leading-relaxed\">문법보다 중요한 것은 명확한 지시입니다.</p></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 space-y-3 group hover:bg-indigo-600 transition-all duration-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-rocket w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors\"><path d=\"M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09z\"></path><path d=\"m12 15-3-3a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.35 22.35 0 0 1-4 2z\"></path><path d=\"M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 0 5 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5\"></path></svg><h4 class=\"text-base font-black dark:text-white group-hover:text-white transition-colors tracking-tight\">반복과 개선</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-bold group-hover:text-indigo-100 transition-colors leading-relaxed\">빠르게 만들고 반복하며 완성도를 높입니다.</p></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 space-y-3 group hover:bg-indigo-600 transition-all duration-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-square-check-big w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors\"><path d=\"M21 10.5V19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h12.5\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg><h4 class=\"text-base font-black dark:text-white group-hover:text-white transition-colors tracking-tight\">동작하는 결과</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-bold group-hover:text-indigo-100 transition-colors leading-relaxed\">완벽한 이해보다 돌아가는 코드가 먼저입니다.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"space-y-8\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight\">이렇게 배우게 됩니다</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/10 text-center space-y-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto shadow-sm text-indigo-600 font-black\">1</div><p class=\"text-sm font-black dark:text-white leading-relaxed\">설명 → 바로 실습 → 결과 확인<br/><span class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">이론보다 경험 중심</span></p></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/10 text-center space-y-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto shadow-sm text-indigo-600 font-black\">2</div><p class=\"text-sm font-black dark:text-white leading-relaxed\">이론 최소, 결과 중심<br/><span class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">최소한의 기본기로 최대 결과</span></p></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/10 text-center space-y-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto shadow-sm text-indigo-600 font-black\">3</div><p class=\"text-sm font-black dark:text-white leading-relaxed\">반복을 통한 정확도 향상<br/><span class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">점진적 완성도 향상</span></p></div></div><p class=\"text-center font-black text-indigo-600 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs\">“보고 이해 → 바로 만들기 → 다시 개선”</p></section><section class=\"space-y-8\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight\">꼭 알고 시작하세요 (기대치 조정)</h2><div class=\"bg-amber-50 dark:bg-amber-500/10 rounded-3xl border border-amber-100 dark:border-amber-500/20 p-8 md:p-10 space-y-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-amber-600\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-alert w-6 h-6\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"8\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12.01\" y1=\"16\" y2=\"16\"></line></svg><span class=\"text-lg font-black tracking-tight\">AI 협업 마인드셋</span></div><ul class=\"space-y-4 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-bold text-sm md:text-base\"><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span>•</span> AI는 완벽하지 않습니다. 비서라고 생각하세요.</li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span>•</span> 한 번에 원하는 결과가 나오지 않을 수 있습니다. 당연한 과정입니다.</li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span>•</span> 결국 결과는 “어떻게 요청하느냐”에 따라 달라집니다.</li></ul><div class=\"pt-4 border-t border-amber-200 dark:border-amber-500/20\"><p class=\"text-center font-black text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-400 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]\">👉 문법보다 대화가 중요합니다</p></div></div></section><section class=\"text-center pt-10\"><button class=\"group bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-500 text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl font-black text-lg shadow-2xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 flex items-center gap-4 mx-auto\">다음 단계: AI 이해하기 <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-6 h-6 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></button></section></div><section class=\"bg-slate-50/50 dark:bg-[#0b0f1a]/50 border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 py-32 overflow-hidden relative\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom,rgba(99,102,241,0.03),transparent_70%)]\"></div><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-4 mb-20 text-center\"><span class=\"text-xs font-black text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 uppercase tracking-[0.3em]\">Full Curriculum</span><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight\">사전 학습 여정 한눈에 보기</h2><div class=\"h-1 w-12 bg-indigo-600 rounded-full\"></div></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"absolute top-8 left-0 w-full h-[1px] bg-slate-200 dark:bg-white/10 hidden lg:block\"></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 lg:grid-cols-10 gap-y-12 lg:gap-4 relative z-10\"><div class=\"group flex flex-col items-center gap-5 cursor-pointer transition-all duration-500 scale-110\"><div class=\"\n                          w-16 h-16 rounded-[1.5rem] flex items-center justify-center border-2 transition-all duration-500 relative\n                          bg-indigo-600 border-indigo-600 text-white shadow-2xl shadow-indigo-600/40 ring-4 ring-indigo-500/10\n                        \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-rocket w-6 h-6 animate-pulse\"><path d=\"M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09z\"></path><path d=\"m12 15-3-3a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.35 22.35 0 0 1-4 2z\"></path><path d=\"M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 0 5 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5\"></path></svg><div class=\"absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-indigo-600 text-xs font-black text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full border-2 border-white dark:border-[#0b0f1a] uppercase tracking-tighter\">Learning</div></div><div class=\"text-center space-y-1.5 px-2\"><p class=\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest transition-colors text-indigo-600\">01</p><p class=\"text-xs font-bold tracking-tight whitespace-nowrap transition-colors text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-black\">시작하기</p></div></div><div class=\"group flex flex-col items-center gap-5 cursor-pointer transition-all duration-500 hover:translate-y-[-4px]\"><div class=\"\n                          w-16 h-16 rounded-[1.5rem] flex items-center justify-center border-2 transition-all duration-500 relative\n                          bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border-slate-100 dark:border-white/10 text-slate-400 group-hover:border-indigo-400 group-hover:text-indigo-600\n                        \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-brain w-6 h-6\"><path d=\"M12 5a3 3 0 1 0-5.997.125 4 4 0 0 0-2.526 5.77 4 4 0 0 0 .556 6.588A4 4 0 1 0 12 18Z\"></path><path d=\"M12 5a3 3 0 1 1 5.997.125 4 4 0 0 1 2.526 5.77 4 4 0 0 1-.556 6.588A4 4 0 1 1 12 18Z\"></path><path d=\"M15 13a4.5 4.5 0 0 1-3-4 4.5 4.5 0 0 1-3 4\"></path><path d=\"M17.599 6.5a3 3 0 0 0 .399-1.375\"></path><path d=\"M6.003 5.125A3 3 0 0 0 6.401 6.5\"></path><path d=\"M3.477 10.896a4 4 0 0 1 .585-.396\"></path><path d=\"M19.938 10.5a4 4 0 0 1 .585.396\"></path><path d=\"M6 18a4 4 0 0 1-1.967-.516\"></path><path d=\"M19.967 17.484A4 4 0 0 1 18 18\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"text-center space-y-1.5 px-2\"><p class=\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest transition-colors text-slate-400\">02</p><p class=\"text-xs font-bold tracking-tight whitespace-nowrap transition-colors text-slate-400\">AI 이해</p></div></div><div class=\"group flex flex-col items-center gap-5 cursor-pointer transition-all duration-500 hover:translate-y-[-4px]\"><div class=\"\n                          w-16 h-16 rounded-[1.5rem] flex items-center justify-center border-2 transition-all duration-500 relative\n                          bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border-slate-100 dark:border-white/10 text-slate-400 group-hover:border-indigo-400 group-hover:text-indigo-600\n                        \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" wi